text: Sam Parsons (born 23 August 1995) is a badminton player from England. Parsons started playing badminton at age five. In 2014, he was the finalist in the English National Badminton Championships in the men's singles event and in 2015 the winner of this event. == Achievements == === BWF International Challenge/Series (5 titles, 1 runner-up) === Men's singles {| class="sortable wikitable" style="font-size: 90%;" !
